| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0114 — Recovery Inhibition (8base)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9f6d14e1-49fd-5f9f-9d97-596dc81ae2ab"
